items.name: red-pump
items.description: A red pump model that is used for AR demonstrations

procedures.name: Replace Pump
procedures.description: Fully animated procedure with no touch interaction.

steps.title: Remove Front Panel
steps.text: Pull on front panel until it snaps away from the pump case.

steps.title: Extract Gear Assembly
steps.text: Decouple the gear assembly from the pump from the and seaparate gears.

steps.title: Rotate Pump to Access Read
steps.text: Rotate the pump to access the back components. Remove the back cover by snapping it off the pump case.

steps.title: Extract the Pump Motor
steps.text: Extract the pump motor to replace.

steps.title: Replace the Pump Motor
steps.text: Replace the pump motor with the new device. Then replace the back cover.

steps.title: Rotate Pump
steps.text: Rotate the pump to access the front components.

steps.title: Reassemble Pump Gears
steps.text: Reassemble the gears and insert them back into the pump.

steps.title: Replace Outer Casing
steps.text: Replace the outer case and ensure a tight fit by snapping components into place.
